ireless setup than I did with a wired one.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eWith the current 58% discount, the Canon PIXMA Inkjet Printer is an excellent value. At just \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Canon-TS6420a-Wireless-Inkjet-Printer/dp/B09TG52XT4?tag=hotoge-20\u0026amp;ascsubtag=UUhtgUeUpU2014766\u0026amp;asc_refurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.howtogeek.com%2Fthis-alexa-compatible-canon-printer-is-58-percent-off%2F\u0026amp;asc_campaign=Affiliate\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer sponsored nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e$59.00 on Amazon\u003c/a\u003e, down from $141, it’s a budget-friendly choice for anyone who needs a reliable all-in-one printer with modern features.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                                            \n\n    \n\n\n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
